            <title>[SPARK-53435] race condition in CachedRDDBuilder</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-53435</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There is race condition between `CachedRDDBuilder.cachedColumnBuffers` and `CachedRDDBuilder.clearCache`: when they interleave each other, `cachedColumnBuffers` might return a `nullptr`.&lt;/p&gt;

